The fork retargets the integration at a local Modelship server (an
OpenAI-compatible API, including the /v1/responses adapter) by adding a
configurable base URL and making the API key optional. To re-sync against a
newer upstream, copy a fresh copy of the component from the pinned tag above
and re-apply the delta set documented in README.md, then bump the merge base.

